# Email Configuration (SMTP - Gmail)
SMTP_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password
SMTP_FROM_EMAIL=your-email@gmail.com

# SMS Configuration (Twilio)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your-twilio-account-sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-twilio-auth-token
TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=+1234567890

# Email Validation API (Optional - AbstractAPI)
EMAIL_VALIDATION_API_KEY=your-email-validation-api-key

# Phone Validation API (Optional - AbstractAPI)
PHONE_VALIDATION_API_KEY=your-phone-validation-api-key

# Instructions:
# 1. Rename this file to .env (remove .example)
# 2. Fill in your actual service credentials
# 3. Add .env to your .gitignore file to keep credentials secure
#
# For Gmail App Password:
# - Enable 2FA on your Google account
# - Generate App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# - Use the generated password, not your regular password
#
# For Twilio:
# - Sign up at https://www.twilio.com/
# - Get your Account SID and Auth Token from Console
# - Purchase a phone number for sending SMS
#
# Validation APIs (Optional):
# - AbstractAPI: https://www.abstractapi.com/
# - If not configured, validation will be skipped
